\v 6 Ama ta ji s«Ěwa m«Ěkaji nyi a shida wu duniya, ba ji na,
\q1 ‚ÄúPat«Ěr waladiňąyar n«Ě Hyal nda dl«Ěv«Ě nyi.‚ÄĚ
